		"description": "<p>Your blood has become suffused with the very stuff of darkness, and when you are injured, it seeps out, obscuring the world around you. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Dexterity, Constitution, or Intelligence increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>You gain darkvision with a range of 60 feet. If you already have darkvision, its range increases by 30 feet instead.</li>\n<li>When you are below your maximum hit points, you are lightly obscured. If you are bloodied, the light level around you drops by one step, from bright light to dim light, and from dim light to darkness. If you are already in darkness when you become bloodied, there is no further effect.</li>\n<li>As long as you are in an area of dim light or darker, one-third of your bloodblade levels count as rogue levels for the purpose of determining your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.4727pnvz5nwn3h23]{Sneak Attack} damage.</li>\n</ul>",
